00:25:29.650 --> 00:25:31.754 align:middle line:84%
More the emotional residues
of lived experience.

00:25:31.754 --> 00:25:32.337 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:25:32.337 --> 00:25:32.836 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:25:32.836 --> 00:25:35.270 align:middle line:84%
>>HANSON: You won't change the
recollection of the events,

00:25:35.270 --> 00:25:36.130 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:25:36.130 --> 00:25:39.050 align:middle line:84%
But you will definitely
