Wow.

00:30:49.752 --> 00:30:53.190 align:middle line:84%
>>HANSON: --where we've
lost touch with ourselves.

00:30:53.190 --> 00:30:55.980 align:middle line:84%
And so just coming back--
this breath, this moment,

00:30:55.980 --> 00:30:56.730 align:middle line:90%
