00:31:14.912 --> 00:31:16.870 align:middle line:84%
So we don't need to get
our knickers in a twist

00:31:16.870 --> 00:31:20.680 align:middle line:84%
so much about this moment,
this sensation, this thought.

00:31:20.680 --> 00:31:21.930 align:middle line:90%
It's kind of streaming along.

00:31:21.930 --> 00:31:22.544 align:middle line:90%
It's there.

00:31:22.544 --> 00:31:24.710 align:middle line:84%
You're not trying to shut
